{
  "messages": [
    {
      "zh": "4-1 免费拥抱（上）",
      "en": "4-1 Free Hugs (part 1)",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "你们回来了。",
      "en": "You’re back.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "......嗯。",
      "en": ".......Yeah.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "——"
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "详细情况我从侦查小队那里了解过了。",
      "en": "I’ve heard about the details from the reconnaissance squad.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "阿米娅，让我检查一下你的手。",
      "en": "Amiya, let me check your hands.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "不用了，凯尔希医生.....",
      "en": "No need for that, Dr.Kal’tsit……",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "阿米娅。",
      "en": "Amiya.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "我，我......",
      "en": "I, I…...",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "......好吧。",
      "en": ".....Okay.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "——"
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "还好。戒指没有裂纹，也没有变色。",
      "en": "Good. The rings neither cracked nor changed color.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "下次就不一定了。",
      "en": "But I’m not sure about next time.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "听着，阿米娅——",
      "en": "Listen, Amiya——",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "小心一点。",
      "en": "Be careful.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "凯尔希医生，我......",
      "en": "Dr.Kal’tsit, I…...",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "......我想休息一下。",
      "en": "......I want to take a rest.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "我理解。去吧。",
      "en": "I understand. You can go now.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "嗯......",
      "en": "Ok…...",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "——"
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "不要再让阿米娅置身这种危险之下了。",
      "en": "Don’t put Amiya in this kind of danger again.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "你也有责任。",
      "en": "You’re responsible as well.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "......Dr.{@nickname}，你去陪陪她。",
      "en": ".......Dr.___, go keep her company.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "别搞砸了。",
      "en": "Don’t mess it up.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "PLAYER",
      "zh": "（敲门）",
      "en": "(Knock the door)",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "门开着。",
      "en": "The door is open.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "......"
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "{@nickname}博士......？",
      "en": "Dr.___……?",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "心事？我吗？",
      "en": "Concerns? Me?",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "......被你发现了呀......哈哈......",
      "en": "......You found out…..haha…...",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "我以为我一直藏得很好呢。",
      "en": "I thought I have hid it well.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "是的，我是有一点心事......就一点点。",
      "en": "Yes, I have a some concerns on my mind…..just a little.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "我已经习惯了这么做了，毕竟不能增加大家的负担呢。",
      "en": "I am used to this already, after all, I can’t add to everyone’s stresses anymore.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "是吧，博士？",
      "en": "Isn’t it, Doctor?",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "......"
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "......我不明白。",
      "en": ".......I don’t understand.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "博士......我不明白。",
      "en": "Doctor.......I don’t understand.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "PLAYER",
      "zh": "（沉默）",
      "en": "(Silence)",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "不，我......我知道我们在做什么。我也知道，牺牲是不可避免的。",
      "en": "No, I…...I know what we are doing. And I also know that sacrifices are unavoidable. ",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "可我......我不知道......",
      "en": "But I…...I don’t know…...",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "为什么我只能看着一个个本该被拯救的生命......在我眼前消逝呢？",
      "en": "Why can I only watch lives that should have been saved……perish before my eyes?",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "为什么......",
      "en": "Why…...",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "真正下手的那个人......是我......呢？",
      "en": "Why am I……the one……that gives the blow? ",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "我知道我身上的责任......我会继续走下去......",
      "en": "I know the responsibilities I have to take….I will keep going...",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "但现在......我真的好累。",
      "en": "But for now…….I’m really tired.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "......"
    },
    {
      "ch": "PLAYER",
      "zh": "（欲言又止）",
      "en": "(Tries to speak)",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "让我一个人静一静吧，{@nickname}博士。",
      "en": "Let me stay alone for a while, Dr.___.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "谢谢你。",
      "en": "Thank you.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "早呀{@nickname}博士。",
      "en": "Good morning, Dr.___.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "咦，凯尔希医生也在吗？",
      "en": "Oh, Dr.Kal’tsit is here too?",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "阿米娅。",
      "en": "Amiya.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "这里有一些比较紧急的任务，需要调用一些人手。",
      "en": "Here are some urgent tasks, we need some hands for them.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "芙兰卡向我提交了报告，提到了她们需要回黑钢复命的事情。",
      "en": "Franka submitted me her report, and mentioned that they need to return to Blacksteel to report for duty.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "还有一些细枝末节的事情，你最好去现场看看。",
      "en": "And there are some more minor chores, you’d better go see for yourself.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "我知道了，我现在就去。",
      "en": "I see, I will go now.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "博士也一起——",
      "en": "Doctor, come with me——",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "我和Dr.{@nickname}还有些事情要谈。",
      "en": "Dr___ and I have somethings to talk about.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "——"
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "我可以旁听吗？",
      "en": "Can I have a listen?",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "不行。",
      "en": "No.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "我可以捂上耳朵——",
      "en": "I can cover my ears—— ",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "不行，去吧。",
      "en": "No, now go.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "呜......",
      "en": "Uhhh…..",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "阿米娅",
      "zh": "凯尔希医生可不许欺负{@nickname}博士哦。",
      "en": "Dr.Kal’tsit, don’t bully Dr.___.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "知道。",
      "en": "I know.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "......你。",
      "en": "......You.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "这么简单的事情都做不到。",
      "en": "Can’t even take care of such an easy thing.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "算了，我已经料到会是这种结果。",
      "en": "Whatever, this is the outcome I expected.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "阿米娅是一个很坚强的孩子。",
      "en": "Amiya is a strong-hearted child.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "但是，过于坚强的外壳，总有一天会——",
      "en": "However, a shell too solid, will one day eventually——",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "————"
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "如果有下次，希望你能稍微发挥点作用。",
      "en": "If this happens again, I hope you can be of some use next time.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "——？",
      "en": "——?",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "怎么了，那个表情。",
      "en": "What’s wrong, that expression of yours.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "PLAYER",
      "zh": "（询问有关戒指的事）",
      "en": "(Ask about the rings)",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "如果阿米娅参与了激烈的战斗——",
      "en": "If Amiya takes part in intense battles——",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "战后，你必须立刻检查她的戒指。",
      "en": "After the battle, you must check her rings immediately.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "戒指产生的任何变化，都要向我报告。",
      "en": "Any changes of the rings must be reported to me.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "其他的，现在还不关你的事。",
      "en": "And the others, are not your business yet.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    },
    {
      "ch": "凯尔希",
      "zh": "——去吧。雷蛇在外面等着护送你。",
      "en": "——Go. Liskarm is waiting outside to escort you.",
      "jp": "",
      "kr": ""
    }
  ]
}
